# Trivy vulnerability suppressions
# Each entry must include a justification.

# CVE-2026-27903 / CVE-2026-27904 — minimatch DoS via glob backtracking
# Located at: usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/node_modules/minimatch
# These CVEs are in minimatch bundled *inside* npm itself (build tooling).
# npm is only present in the image to install production deps during Docker build;
# it is never invoked at runtime and is not accessible to external users.
# minimatch@10.2.4 (fix) is published, but npm@11.11.0 (latest as of 2026-03-06)
# still bundles minimatch@10.2.2 — awaiting an npm release that picks up 10.2.4.
CVE-2026-27903
CVE-2026-27904
